OL,5, The Post Office chairman has stepped   
OL,6, down amid ongoing tensions after the   
OL,7, Horizon IT scandal that saw hundreds of
OL,8, sub-postmasters wrongly convicted.     
OL,10,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch said  
OL,11,Fshe and Henry Staunton parted ways with
OL,12,Fmutual consent, as the Post Office was 
OL,13,Funder heightened scrutiny and she "felt
OL,14,Fthere was a need for new leadership".  
OL,16,FBut the Post Office said in a statement
OL,17,Fthat he had been asked to leave.       
OL,19,FAn interim chair is expected to be     
OL,20,Fappointed shortly.                     
